N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1221.7 - Placing of articles on exterior window sills prohibited

State Regulations

The occupant shall not place any parcel, bottle or other
article on the exterior part of any window sill in the
terminal. Notes
